<h1 data-section-id="15neh6j" data-start="3305" data-end="3333">STEP 11 — Cloudinary Setup</h1>
<p data-start="3335" data-end="3350">Create account:</p>
<p data-start="3352" data-end="3389"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a target="_blank" class="decorated-link" rel="noopener" href="https://cloudinary.com/?utm_source=chatgpt.com">Cloudinary Official Website<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2cb00440.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></span></p>
<p data-start="3391" data-end="3403">Then create:</p>
