You want to build a public political/social organization website like:</p>
<ul data-start="109" data-end="214">
<li data-section-id="1s60gi7" data-start="109" data-end="133">
<p data-start="111" data-end="133">Youth movement website</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p1kg1n" data-start="134" data-end="158">
<p data-start="136" data-end="158">Political party portal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cjl1kg" data-start="159" data-end="186">
<p data-start="161" data-end="186">Public grievance platform</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1czna07" data-start="187" data-end="214">
<p data-start="189" data-end="214">Social awareness platform</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="216" data-end="261">for <strong data-start="220" data-end="261"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Bihar Naujawan Sabha</span></span></strong></p>
<p data-start="263" data-end="276">Users should:</p>
<ul data-start="277" data-end="435">
<li data-section-id="6gu77a" data-start="277" data-end="298">
<p data-start="279" data-end="298">Visit without login</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="120jd9t" data-start="299" data-end="316">
<p data-start="301" data-end="316">Read posts/news</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s1tkq9" data-start="317" data-end="336">
<p data-start="319" data-end="336">Join organization</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vx00bl" data-start="337" data-end="361">
<p data-start="339" data-end="361">Submit problems/issues</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rxphnx" data-start="362" data-end="378">
<p data-start="364" data-end="378">Register/Login</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f2sxzs" data-start="379" data-end="404">
<p data-start="381" data-end="404">Share public complaints</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="85wvx0" data-start="405" data-end="420">
<p data-start="407" data-end="420">Upload photos</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xlffj" data-start="421" data-end="435">
<p data-start="423" data-end="435">Like/comment</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="437" data-end="497">This is a strong real-world MERN project for your portfolio.</p>
<h1 data-section-id="1ngdlb1" data-start="499" data-end="530">Recommended Website Structure</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="vrl9z8" data-start="532" data-end="547">Public Pages</h2>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="549" data-end="809" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="549" data-end="567"><tr data-start="549" data-end="567"><th data-start="549" data-end="556" data-col-size="sm" class="last:pe-10">Page</th><th data-start="556" data-end="567" data-col-size="sm" class="last:pe-10">Purpose</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="578" data-end="809"><tr data-start="578" data-end="607"><td data-start="578" data-end="585" data-col-size="sm">Home</td><td data-start="585" data-end="607" data-col-size="sm">Organization intro</td></tr><tr data-start="608" data-end="641"><td data-start="608" data-end="619" data-col-size="sm">About Us</td><td data-start="619" data-end="641" data-col-size="sm">Mission &amp; ideology</td></tr><tr data-start="642" data-end="671"><td data-start="642" data-end="652" data-col-size="sm">Join Us</td><td data-start="652" data-end="671" data-col-size="sm">Membership form</td></tr><tr data-start="672" data-end="714"><td data-start="672" data-end="690" data-col-size="sm">Public Problems</td><td data-start="690" data-end="714" data-col-size="sm">People submit issues</td></tr><tr data-start="715" data-end="742"><td data-start="715" data-end="725" data-col-size="sm">Gallery</td><td data-start="725" data-end="742" data-col-size="sm">Photos/videos</td></tr><tr data-start="743" data-end="782"><td data-start="743" data-end="757" data-col-size="sm">Latest News</td><td data-start="757" data-end="782" data-col-size="sm">Posts &amp; announcements</td></tr><tr data-start="783" data-end="809"><td data-start="783" data-end="793" data-col-size="sm">Contact</td><td data-start="793" data-end="809" data-col-size="sm">Contact form</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="relative h-0 self-end select-none"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-toke