<p data-start="1188" data-end="1222">Admin can review all applications.</p>
<hr data-start="1224" data-end="1227">
<h1 data-section-id="16mavz1" data-start="1229" data-end="1265">4. Public Problem Reporting System</h1>
<p data-start="1267" data-end="1303">Users/public can report issues like:</p>
<ul data-start="1304" data-end="1405">
<li data-section-id="18nfym5" data-start="1304" data-end="1316">
<p data-start="1306" data-end="1316">Corruption</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1131ccb" data-start="1317" data-end="1335">
<p data-start="1319" data-end="1335">College problems</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17zhn0a" data-start="1336" data-end="1349">
<p data-start="1338" data-end="1349">Road issues</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ov6e4l" data-start="1350" data-end="1370">
<p data-start="1352" data-end="1370">Electricity issues</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1twrfol" data-start="1371" data-end="1387">
<p data-start="1373" data-end="1387">Water problems</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15epjql" data-start="1388" data-end="1405">
<p data-start="1390" data-end="1405">Education scams</p>
</li>
</ul>
