You want a controlled political/social website for <strong data-start="63" data-end="104"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Bihar Naujawan Sabha</span></span></strong> where:</p>
<p data-start="113" data-end="228">❌ Users CANNOT post anything publicly<br data-start="150" data-end="153">
❌ Users CANNOT upload random content<br data-start="189" data-end="192">
❌ Users CANNOT create public posts</p>
<p data-start="230" data-end="245">Only ADMIN can:</p>
<ul data-start="246" data-end="313">
<li data-section-id="1ycwm1z" data-start="246" data-end="260">
<p data-start="248" data-end="260">Create posts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="85wvx0" data-start="261" data-end="276">
<p data-start="263" data-end="276">Upload photos</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18st8ny" data-start="277" data-end="291">
<p data-start="279" data-end="291">Publish news</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="n58wyf" data-start="292" data-end="313">
<p data-start="294" data-end="313">Share announcements</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="315" data-end="339">But public visitors CAN:</p>
<ul data-start="340" data-end="459">
<li data-section-id="18bf86a" data-start="340" data-end="355">
<p data-start="342" data-end="355">Visit website</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="120jd9t" data-start="356" data-end="373">
<p data-start="358" data-end="373">Read posts/news</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="123fyol" data-start="374" data-end="393">
<p data-start="376" data-end="393">Fill Join Us form</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o8mdfc" data-start="394" data-end="431">
<p data-start="396" data-end="431">Submit problems/issues/contact form</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n6q41u" data-start="432" data-end="459">
<p data-start="434" data-end="459">Register/Login (optional)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="461" data-end="507">That is actually a better and safer structure.</p>
<h1 data-section-id="17cq2is" data-start="509" data-end="534">Final Website Structure</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1q1yb8q" data-start="536" data-end="555">Public Users Can</h2>
<p data-start="557" data-end="686">✅ View website<br data-start="571" data-end="574">
✅ Read announcements<br data-start="594" data-end="597">
✅ Read news/posts<br data-start="614" data-end="617">
✅ View gallery<br data-start="631" data-end="634">
✅ Submit complaints/problems<br data-start="662" data-end="665">
✅ Join organization</p>
<hr data-start="688" data-end="691">
<h1 data-section-id="2sqf7p" data-start="693" data-end="704">Admin Can</h1>
<p data-start="706" data-end="818">✅ Create posts<br data-start="720" data-end="723">
✅ Upload images<br data-start="738" data-end="741">
✅ Approve/reject issues<br data-start="764" data-end="767">
✅ Manage users<br data-start="781" data-end="784">
✅ Delete spam<br data-start="797" data-end="800">
✅ Manage gallery</p>
