essages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="75d22c43-3d2c-470f-993b-2dbf64aeae34" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="144">Now I completely understand your idea 👍<br data-start="40" data-end="43">
You want a modern political/social media style website for <strong data-start="102" data-end="143"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Bihar Naujawan Sabha</span></span></strong>.</p>
<p data-start="146" data-end="175">NOT a simple gallery website.</p>
<p data-start="177" data-end="201">You want something like:</p>
<ul data-start="203" data-end="360">
<li data-section-id="kwr6a9" data-start="203" data-end="225">
<p data-start="205" data-end="225">Facebook-style posts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1q3wlgj" data-start="226" data-end="245">
<p data-start="228" data-end="245">Political updates</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vd36or" data-start="246" data-end="266">
<p data-start="248" data-end="266">Public issue posts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p182ft" data-start="267" data-end="287">
<p data-start="269" data-end="287">Photo + text posts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vefknp" data-start="288" data-end="301">
<p data-start="290" data-end="301">Like button</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hdhoer" data-start="302" data-end="316">
<p data-start="304" data-end="316">Share button</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fu7ry" data-start="317" data-end="333">
<p data-start="319" data-end="333">Comment system</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6ay1yw" data-start="334" data-end="360">
<p data-start="336" data-end="360">Admin-controlled posting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="362" data-end="366">But:</p>
<p data-start="368" data-end="482">❌ Public users cannot create posts<br data-start="402" data-end="405">
✅ Only admin creates posts<br data-start="431" data-end="434">
✅ Public can interact (like/share/comment maybe)</p>
<hr data-start="484" data-end="487">
<h1 data-section-id="v5yv4o" data-start="489" data-end="509">FINAL WEBSITE IDEA</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="skwqiw" data-start="511" data-end="523">Home Feed</h2>
<p data-start="525" data-end="552">Website homepage will show:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="554" data-end="657"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2cb00440.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>[ Post Image ]</span><br><span>[ Post Title ]</span><br><span>[ Post Description ]</span><br><br><span>❤️ Like</span><br><span>💬 Comment</span><br><span>📤 Share</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="659" data-end="672">Exactly like:</p>
<ul data-start="673" data-end="718">
<li data-section-id="6htwxs" data-start="673" data-end="683">
<p data-start="675" data-end="683">Facebook</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="b7govk" data-start="684" data-end="695">
<p data-start="686" data-end="695">Instagram</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pki8su" data-start="696" data-end="718">
<p data-start="698" data-end="718">Political news pages</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="720" data-end="723">
<h1 data-section-id="1j4j5t5" data-start="725" data-end="743">Public Users Can</h1>
<p data-start="745" data-end="855">✅ View posts<br data-start="757" data-end="760">
✅ Like posts<br data-start="772" data-end="775">
✅ Share posts<br data-start="788" data-end="791">
✅ Comment (optional)<br data-start="811" data-end="814">
✅ Submit problems<br data-start="831" data-end="834">
✅ Join organization</p>
<p data-start="857" data-end="861">BUT:</p>
<p data-start="863" data-end="912">❌ Cannot create posts<br data-start="884" data-end="887">
❌ Cannot upload content</p>
<hr data-start="914" data-end="917">
<h1 data-section-id="w1uvo1" data-start="919" data-end="935">ONLY ADMIN CAN</h1>
<p data-start="937" data-end="1039">✅ Create posts<br data-start="951" data-end="954">
✅ Upload photos<br data-start="969" data-end="972">
✅ Add announcements<br data-start="991" data-end="994">
✅ Delete posts<br data-start="1008" data-end="1011">
✅ Manage comments/problems</p>
<hr data-start="1041" data-end="1044">
<h1 data-section-id="wkecsf" data-start="1046" data-end="1073">Recommended Main Features</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="wrmk1g" data-start="1075" data-end="1102">1. Political Feed System</h2>
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1123">Each post contains:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1125" data-end="1226"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky top-(--sticky-padding-top) z-2 select-none"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2cb00440.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2cb00440.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><d