<p data-start="58" data-end="91">Because your site needs to store:</p>
<ul data-start="93" data-end="177">
<li data-section-id="cij370" data-start="93" data-end="106">
<p data-start="95" data-end="106">Admin posts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1b1tq4z" data-start="107" data-end="120">
<p data-start="109" data-end="120">Likes count</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="73wyvd" data-start="121" data-end="136">
<p data-start="123" data-end="136">Join Us forms</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="de2vtk" data-start="137" data-end="158">
<p data-start="139" data-end="158">Problem submissions</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1op1b90" data-start="159" data-end="177">
<p data-start="161" data-end="177">Admin login data</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="179" data-end="304">Without MongoDB:<br>
❌ Data will disappear on refresh/server restart<br data-start="243" data-end="246">
❌ No permanent storage<br data-start="268" data-end="271">
❌ No real backend functionality</p>
<hr data-start="306" data-end="309">
<h1 data-section-id="10xdny1" data-start="311" data-end="334">When You Need MongoDB</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="zs3msz" data-start="336" data-end="348">Right Now</h2>
<p data-start="349" data-end="369">You can first build:</p>
<ul data-start="370" data-end="418">
<li data-section-id="1t2ziqo" data-start="370" data-end="378">
<p data-start="372" data-end="378">Navbar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="issxu9" data-start="379" data-end="393">
<p data-start="381" data-end="393">Hero section</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="yyth2e" data-start="394" data-end="405">
<p data-start="396" data-end="405">UI design</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19l9k5z" data-start="406" data-end="418">
<p data-start="408" data-end="418">Post cards</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="420" data-end="436">WITHOUT MongoDB.</p>
<p data-start="438" data-end="471">That is okay for frontend design.</p>
<hr data-start="473" data-end="476">
<h1 data-section-id="h4zocr" data-start="478" data-end="514">But Later You MUST Connect MongoDB</h1>
<p data-start="516" data-end="556">Because your website needs dynamic data:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="558" data-end="694" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="558" data-end="586"><tr data-start="558" data-end="586"><th data-start="558" data-end="568" data-col-size="sm" class="last:pe-10">Feature</th><th data-start="568" data-end="586" data-col-size="sm" class="last:pe-10">Needs MongoDB?</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="597" data-end="694"><tr data-start="597" data-end="616"><td data-start="597" data-end="611" data-col-size="sm">Admin posts</td><td data-start="611" data-end="616" data-col-size="sm">✅</td></tr><tr data-start="617" data-end="630"><td data-start="617" data-end="625" data-col-size="sm">Likes</td><td data-start="625" data-end="630" data-col-size="sm">✅</td></tr><tr data-start="631" data-end="652"><td data-start="631" data-end="647" data-col-size="sm">Problem forms</td><td data-start="647" data-end="652" data-col-size="sm">✅</td></tr><tr data-start="653" data-end="674"><td data-start="653" data-end="669" data-col-size="sm">Join Us forms</td><td data-start="669" data-end="674" data-col-size="sm">✅</td></tr><tr data-start="675" data-end="694"><td data-start="675" data-end="689" data-col-size="sm">Admin login</td><td data-start="689" data-end="694" data-col-size="sm">✅</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="relative h-0 self-end select-none"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary relative z-10 my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2cb00440.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="696" data-end="699">
<h1 data-section-id="16ikxlx" data-start="701" data-end="728">Recommended Order For You</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1hbxhtn" data-start="730" data-end="756">First Build Frontend UI</h2>
<ul data-start="757" data-end="801">
<li data-section-id="1t2ziqo" data-start="757" data-end="765">
<p data-start="759" data-end="765">Navbar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="issxu9" data-start="766" data-end="780">
<p data-start="768" data-end="780">Hero section</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19l9k5z" data-start="781" data-end="793">
<p data-start="783" data-end="793">Post cards</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="170jq5p" data-start="794" data-end="801">
<p data-start="796" data-end="801">Forms</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="803" data-end="808">THEN:</p>
<h2 data-section-id="u42f6e" data-start="810" data-end="838">Connect Backend + MongoDB</h2>
<p data-start="840" data-end="878">This is actually easier for beginners.</p>
<hr data-start="880" data-end="883">
<h1 data-section-id="1crg4xr" data-start="885" data-end="925">For Now You Can Continue Frontend Only</h1>
<p data-start="927" data-end="945">Your current goal:</p>
<p data-start="947" data-end="1041">✅ Beautiful homepage<br data-start="967" data-end="970">
✅ Political UI<br data-start="984" data-end="987">
✅ Post card design<br data-start="1005" data-end="1008">
✅ Join Us form<br data-start="1022" data-end="1025">
✅ Problem form</p>
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1086">After UI complete:<br>
👉 connect backend APIs.</p>
<hr data-start="1088" data-end="1091">
<h1 data-section-id="1xo0cn0" data-start="1093" data-end="1119">Later MongoDB Connection</h1>
<p data-start="1121" data-end="1142">In backend/server.js:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1144" data-end="1205"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky top-(--sticky-padding-top) z-2 select-none"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2cb00440.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-2cb00440.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><d